# Review feedback priority

When addressing PR review feedback:

1. **SonarQube / SonarCloud takes highest priority.** Fix Quality Gate failures and Sonar issues (reliability, security, bugs, hotspots that fail the gate) before anything else.
2. **Copilot review comments can be ignored** unless they independently match a Sonar finding or an obvious correctness bug you would fix anyway.
